description: Demolition and redevelopment of the existing building and the erection of a part 15, part 16-24, part 19-27 storey building to provide a residential led mixed use development comprising ground floor cafe/restaurant uses (A3); office (B1); residents gym and members lounge; and 253 residential units, together with ancillary residential facilities, associated amenity space, car, motorcycle and cycle parking, access and servicing, refuse storage and collection facilities and landscaped public piazza
